lead_paragraph: Japan's Haru Nomura produced a strong finish on the tougher back nine to take a three-shot lead after the second round at the Swinging Skirts LPGA Classic in San Francisco on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Steady Nomura Moves Three Strokes Clear in San Francisco
